          p Life Stream is Quantifie Self data aggregator platform. I started working on this project as part of my final passion project at the <a href="http://www.thisismetis.com/">Metis Data Science Bootcamp</a> program. The goal of the platform was to automate pulling data from a variety of sources including Fitbit, Moves, Mint, and social media sites for example, aggregating it, and preparing it for analysis in near real-time.

